Fig: <Bold> Property Dialog Demo </Bold>
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Features:</Paragraph>
<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Run-time customization of chart properties and inner controls.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>
<Paragraph FontWeight="Bold" FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="16">
Interactive Features:</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Click <Bold>"Property Dialog" </Bold> button to show the Properties dialog.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Select the <Bold>"Show ToolBar"</Bold> check box to display a toolbar from which the Properties dialog can be invoked.</Paragraph>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph>Change the property values of the chart and inner controls through the Properties dialog.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Chart"</Bold> tab shows the list of Chart properties.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Chart Area"</Bold> tab shows the list of Chart Area properties.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Chart Series"</Bold> tab shows the list of Chart Series properties.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Chart Axis"</Bold> tab shows the list of Chart Axis properties.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Chart Legend"</Bold> tab shows the legend properties.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph>The <Bold>"Annotations labels"</Bold> tab shows the list of Annotations properties. </Paragraph>
</ListItem>
</List>



